drivers: net: xgene: Enable MDIO driver

This patch enables MDIO driver by,

- Selecting MDIO_XGENE
- Changed open and close to use phy_start and phy_stop
- Changed to use mac_ops->tx(rx)_enable and tx(rx)_disable

